{"tid":721212,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大數據技術，可否解決目前醫學問題","createTime":"2018-06-28T14:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T17:53:24.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa297364d511a57cf56b669772fe7dd9280bbd6","tid":721212,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:27:55.000Z","msg":"其實現在的醫學研究報告和文獻，臨床測試，都係搵幾百人出黎試，sample size得幾百人。<br />\n<br />\n如果用大數據，用 internet 和 big data，去聯繫和分析病人情況，例如分析病人的病歷，和他分享出黎的facebook post和，ig post，再做survey，再用埋人工智能去分析，sample size 可以幾百萬人，咁拿出黎的數據，會否比雙盲對照研究可靠？<br />\n<br />\n不過涉及私隱問題<br />\n<br />\n同埋要it公司，政府，法律，醫院，醫學研究界合作。"},{"pid":"643c9d7245128f1de4129368738ba70d4f9f7d19","tid":721212,"uid":30454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:30:06.000Z","msg":"但係有d病既病徵好相似<br />\n我覺得的確有幫助 但唔會完全解決"},{"pid":"0ab07cd5eb77fb709a1f4313b4be9ed6a5b4f978","tid":721212,"uid":7837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:30:32.000Z","msg":"big data會係未來醫學大方向"},{"pid":"182a3c261469240544103ac4f3235cc7b54c18f0","tid":721212,"uid":51677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:31:50.000Z","msg":"有都唔會普及<br />\n個世界已經愈來愈多人"},{"pid":"1b0ed03142d141cc31b939a149010875071432fb","tid":721212,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"唔太可行. 因為諗下點解simple size 會有所限制 而唔係無限大"},{"pid":"11b48dff28ff37cdeb55018801bfa577f83372b6","tid":721212,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1b0ed03142d141cc31b939a149010875071432fb","tid":721212,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"唔太可行. 因為諗下點解simple size 會有所限制 而唔係無限大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:54:41.000Z","msg":"咁易搵到人做實驗？傳統研究成本高？"},{"pid":"e2dd0dad0934bfcb58691b7c260e88300bdb74e9","tid":721212,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T14:55:38.000Z","msg":"Expert system<img